snippet.title: Rogue Ascent Official Trailer - Available on App Labs
snippet.description:
Download Rogue Ascent on App Labs! https://clique.games/applabsra
Join the Discord: https://clique.games/radiscord
Website: https://rogueascent.com

Rogue Ascent VR is a Procedurally-Generated Sci-Fi Shooter controlled seamlessly by Meta Quest hand-tracking technology. Discover and combine countless weapons types, attachment modifications, abilities, gadgets, perks, and powerups as you blast and beguile past teams of formidable foes. The finished gameplay experience will features many added items, secrets, perks, abilities, enemy types, game modes, bosses, biomes, achievements, and competitive online leaderboards!
